\end{table}

There was a typo when 50 was entered into the dataset when the value should have been 30.  The value 50 will pull the \emph{mean} to the right. 

  \end{itemize}
  
\item Left-skewed: presence of relatively low values 
  \begin{itemize}
  \item 
  % Requires the booktabs if the memoir class is not being used
  \begin{table}[htbp]
